==English==

===Noun===
'''[[black]] [[widow]]''' (''Plural:'' '''black widows''')
{{wikipedia}}

#A species of [[venomous]] [[spider]]. The bite is painful to humans and occasionally fatal. The females are marked by a red [[hourglass]] shape on the [[abdomen]].

====Scientific names====
*''[[Latrodectus mactans]]''

